data.text: The text to display on the ux-flex-video component
data.src: Is the source URL for the video. e.g. //www.youtube.com/embed/aiBt44rrslw
data.height: Is the height of the iframe
data.width: Is the width of the iframe
data.frameborder: Is the frameborder of the iframe
data.allowfullscreen: Allow full screen options.  e.g. allowfullscreen webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen
